txt.en: 'The farmhouse is rebuilt, but there is still a great deal of repair to do. The wind-mills do not have blades, and the farmhouses themselves are empty shells. We are getting close, but we are still not there yet.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
